Purpose
In this assignment, you will apply your knowledge of Python classes and packages to develop a simple IT Help Desk Management System.
This system will allow users to create, manage, and track IT support tickets. The objective is to understand object-oriented programming (OOP)
concepts such as class creation, object instantiation, methods, attributes, and encapsulation, as well as modular programming using Python packages.

By completing this assignment, you will develop real-world problem-solving skills relevant to IT support roles, commonly found in organizations.
